STATE
v.
Royal Lee BERRY. No. 116P07-2. Supreme Court of North Carolina. October 11, 2007. Daniel P. O'Brien, Assistant Attorney General, Peter S. Gilchrist, III, District Attorney, for State of NC.

The following order has been entered on the motion filed on the 7th day of September 2007 by Defendant for Discretionary Review:
